column7: ⭒ PRICES ⭒ Dinner (vegetarian/vegan): 45 kr. Standard concert and club night ticket: 95 DKK Stars and super supporters concert and club night ticket: 140 DKK Reduced price available upon request, write to mie@detturkisetelt.dk Tickets for dinner + concert and club night available at the door until sold out.
column9: ⭒ FLINTA ⭒ FLINTA is an acronym for female, lesbian, intersex, non-binary, trans and agender. This event is for flinta people only. We never assume anyone’s gender identity, but we will inform all our guests about the guidelines at the door. We create FLINTA-only events to offer a safer space and community working against oppressive structures.
column10: hyggelig fællesmiddag, høj energi koncerter, festlig, hyggelig, cute, fun.
column11: Der er kørestolsadgang, adgang fra stueplan. Der er ikke noget chillrum for folk der er overstimulerede, men mulighed for at komme op på et kontor og tage en pause.
column13: We invite all flinta*s on a rollercoaster ride from emo to euphoria, from vulnerable to L✪L, from beautiful to fugly. Plant-based community dinner, Ponny punk, Paydar frenzy and DJ Dogmother’s hard bass. Everything that nourishes the heart.
column14: ⭒ SAFER SPACE ⭒ We aim to create a safer space, and our safer space hosts will be present throughout the evening. We do not tolerate any form of discrimination, harassment or oppressive behavior.
